  "detailed_description": "Get ready to face countless waves of relentless enemies <br>with powerful weapons and strategically placed turrets at your disposal<br>whether you're flying solo or teaming up with friends in co-op mode<br>So jump in, gear up, and let the mayhem begin!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/aa724b4c7a190298799dd3ea5113cbee.avif?t=1726499305\" width=300 height=75 /></span><br>Defend your base against incoming threats by using your weapons and building defenses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/a41b70ff9537f4eb5872fd4627538015.poster.avif?t=1726499305\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/a41b70ff9537f4eb5872fd4627538015.webm?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/a41b70ff9537f4eb5872fd4627538015.mp4?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/3055554fdf063bf53318b8a8c1e4b6aa.avif?t=1726499305\" width=300 height=75 /></span><br>Need more firepower? Okay.<br>Set up a defense turret and slow down those enemies <br>with barricades and other sweet obstacles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/9da18de9b4da4b7697dca880f2dd28f7.poster.avif?t=1726499305\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/9da18de9b4da4b7697dca880f2dd28f7.webm?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/9da18de9b4da4b7697dca880f2dd28f7.mp4?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/af931a98e741892db8a579800dfa67d6.avif?t=1726499305\" width=300 height=75 /></span><br>Hey, look! your friends are here!<br>play with your friends up to 24 players<br>brainstorm plans, ideas, skills, and firepower<br>to stop the enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/b180b635cb2bcf0e09506e1b47d3f361.poster.avif?t=1726499305\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/b180b635cb2bcf0e09506e1b47d3f361.webm?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/b180b635cb2bcf0e09506e1b47d3f361.mp4?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/fd0d456e9a043a9e69f658e4075e965b.avif?t=1726499305\" width=300 height=75 /></span><br>take on a never-ending wave of enemies<br>that randomly generates each run you play. <br>fight until the game crashes and let's see how long you can last!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/4e4eb003e0daca9e041bf7bf098326b3.poster.avif?t=1726499305\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/4e4eb003e0daca9e041bf7bf098326b3.webm?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/4e4eb003e0daca9e041bf7bf098326b3.mp4?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/47e1800c41df4d19d7b9d18b139b77dc.avif?t=1726499305\" width=300 height=75 /></span><br>Hey there! It's great to meet you! My name is Non <br>and I'm a solo game developer from Thailand. <br>I'm super excited to let you know that I've just created my very first game, <br>and I can't wait for you to try it out! <br><br>I want to be honest with you though: <br>there might be a few features that are missing,<br>like control customization and controller support. <br>But I really hope you'll still enjoy playing it! <br>Your support means the world to me and <br>will help me lay the foundation for future projects, including Playground Mayhem. <br><br>Thank you so much for taking the time to check it out! I really appreciate it!",
  "about_the_game": "Get ready to face countless waves of relentless enemies <br>with powerful weapons and strategically placed turrets at your disposal<br>whether you're flying solo or teaming up with friends in co-op mode<br>So jump in, gear up, and let the mayhem begin!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/aa724b4c7a190298799dd3ea5113cbee.avif?t=1726499305\" width=300 height=75 /></span><br>Defend your base against incoming threats by using your weapons and building defenses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/a41b70ff9537f4eb5872fd4627538015.poster.avif?t=1726499305\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/a41b70ff9537f4eb5872fd4627538015.webm?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/a41b70ff9537f4eb5872fd4627538015.mp4?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/3055554fdf063bf53318b8a8c1e4b6aa.avif?t=1726499305\" width=300 height=75 /></span><br>Need more firepower? Okay.<br>Set up a defense turret and slow down those enemies <br>with barricades and other sweet obstacles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/9da18de9b4da4b7697dca880f2dd28f7.poster.avif?t=1726499305\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/9da18de9b4da4b7697dca880f2dd28f7.webm?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/9da18de9b4da4b7697dca880f2dd28f7.mp4?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/af931a98e741892db8a579800dfa67d6.avif?t=1726499305\" width=300 height=75 /></span><br>Hey, look! your friends are here!<br>play with your friends up to 24 players<br>brainstorm plans, ideas, skills, and firepower<br>to stop the enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/b180b635cb2bcf0e09506e1b47d3f361.poster.avif?t=1726499305\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/b180b635cb2bcf0e09506e1b47d3f361.webm?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/b180b635cb2bcf0e09506e1b47d3f361.mp4?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/fd0d456e9a043a9e69f658e4075e965b.avif?t=1726499305\" width=300 height=75 /></span><br>take on a never-ending wave of enemies<br>that randomly generates each run you play. <br>fight until the game crashes and let's see how long you can last!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/4e4eb003e0daca9e041bf7bf098326b3.poster.avif?t=1726499305\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/4e4eb003e0daca9e041bf7bf098326b3.webm?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/4e4eb003e0daca9e041bf7bf098326b3.mp4?t=1726499305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/47e1800c41df4d19d7b9d18b139b77dc.avif?t=1726499305\" width=300 height=75 /></span><br>Hey there! It's great to meet you! My name is Non <br>and I'm a solo game developer from Thailand. <br>I'm super excited to let you know that I've just created my very first game, <br>and I can't wait for you to try it out! <br><br>I want to be honest with you though: <br>there might be a few features that are missing,<br>like control customization and controller support. <br>But I really hope you'll still enjoy playing it! <br>Your support means the world to me and <br>will help me lay the foundation for future projects, including Playground Mayhem. <br><br>Thank you so much for taking the time to check it out! I really appreciate it!",
